column1: Table S3. Known phosphorylation/dephosphorylation events, assembled from the literature

Phosphorylation events that are known to depend on a kinase regulatory protein. The kinase regulatory protein (column A/B) associates with the kinase (columnC/D) to phosphorylate the substrate (column E/F)

Dephosphorylation events that are known to depend on a phosphatase regulatory protein. The phosphatase regulatory protein (column A/B) associates with the phosphatase (columnC/D) to dephosphorylate the substrate (column E/F)
